movement
	
	go_out_parenthesis	'f)a'

a class of special operations that
reshape a block of text
delineated by a double quotation 
and current cursor's position

	to_sharp		':?^"$?+1,.-1s/^/# /:\?d:\/d' 

new information from enviroment

	insert_date		':r! date +"\%d \%B \%y"kJA'
	read_from		':r! '

exit
	exit_with_save		':wq'

